387
00:20:40,079 --> 00:20:40,880
Go, Ms. Li.

388
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:42,275
Go, go.

389
00:20:51,100 --> 00:20:52,119
Zhixiao,

390
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:54,350
don't be angry with your father.

391
00:20:54,675 --> 00:20:56,675
