483
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:57,500
I invited Xi.

484
00:25:57,839 --> 00:25:58,439
Mom.

485
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:00,119
Aunt.

486
00:26:00,119 --> 00:26:00,800
Mm.

