697
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:40,639
Thank you. Put them in.

698
00:34:40,639 --> 00:34:42,239
Oh, and a hot drink, too.

699
00:34:43,150 --> 00:34:44,000
Thank you.

700
00:34:46,275 --> 00:34:48,550
