719
00:36:04,225 --> 00:36:05,575
Don't you have

720
00:36:06,250 --> 00:36:08,320
professional advice for a painful period

721
00:36:08,919 --> 00:36:10,975
as a doctor?

722
00:36:13,275 --> 00:36:14,520
I'm afraid

723
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:16,159
